<subSubSection id="FEEBE8D1650138EA2F304AF10C1E5CB4" pageId="12" pageNumber="43" type="comments">
<paragraph id="BBB84F6CBD57A02A326125C3DA33955B" pageId="12" pageNumber="43">Comments.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2F658C53EBCEC90BBB17910A4AB4D3AF" pageId="12" pageNumber="43">
<taxonomicName id="84A10A01DFFCDFDECA2E65672CCE834B" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Megachile lippiae" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="43" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lippiae">Megachile lippiae</taxonomicName>
was originally described as a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="A22B25829C7790AC64857ABEA4BE3A18" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Megachile texana" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="43" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="texana">Megachile texana</taxonomicName>
(Mitchell, 1935). It was raised to species level by 
<bibRefCitation id="2616F2FF5F1F74D1939E22B11512106E" author="Sheffield, CS" journalOrPublisher="Canadian Journal of Arthropod Identification" pageId="22" pageNumber="53" title="Leafcutter and Mason Bees of the Genus Megachile Latreille (Hymenoptera: Megachilidae) in Canada and Alaska." url="10.3752/cjai.2011.18." volume="18" year="2011">Sheffield et al. (2011)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<taxonomicName id="FD03815EB09A5CEA0CB070A921A58C0A" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Megachile lippiae" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="43" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lippiae">Megachile lippiae</taxonomicName>
is primarily a western North American species, though records exist from eastern localities (Figure 11). 
<taxonomicName id="7A4E8A00900D34170330DC76A1467AE2" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Megachile schismatura" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="43" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="schismatura">Megachile schismatura</taxonomicName>
is removed from synonymy under 
<taxonomicName id="1630B97E2FFA7993EBCD0C8393205ABC" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Megachile texana" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="43" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="texana">Megachile texana</taxonomicName>
and placed as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="36D3FE94F9608D9F34DCD4A26CC62AAF" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Megachile lippiae" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="43" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lippiae">Megachile lippiae</taxonomicName>
herein.
</paragraph>
